The sid is obfuscated. To calculate it, first compute `(id << 8) ^ 0xc3c3c3`; then convert that number to decimal and replace the digits 0-9 with a-j. For pokemon, compute `(national_id << 16 | form_id << 8) ^ 0xc3c3c3`.

